        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_48\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre11\"><span class=\"text_3\">Deleuze G. Anti-oedipus[M]. A&amp;C Black, </span><span class=\"text_3\">2004: 239-240.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_55\"><span class=\"text_5\">述加速主义的基本理念。如兰德所言“加速的全部任务在于德勒兹所谓解域” <sup class=\"calibre13\">①</sup></span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_56\"><span class=\"text_19\">因此机器革命必须与社会主义调控背道而驰朝着更无拘束的、正在 拆毁社会领域的市场化进程推进在“市场运动、解码和解域”上走得“更 远”以及“在解域的方向上走得再远也不够你还没看到任何东西”。</span><span class=\"text_20\">② </span><span class=\"text_21\">(</span><span class=\"text_22\">Machinic Desire</span><span class=\"text_21\">)</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_52\"><span class=\"text_5\">据此可以说尼克•兰德所谓“加速主义”“加”的是市场运转、资本流动 和科技发展的“速”借以突破国家、政治制度、社会组织、法律等“人类安全 系统”的停滞状态其最终目的是加速冲向最后的大爆炸也就是说加速人类 文明的毁灭兰德以一种狂暴而谵妄的写作来实现这些理念他几乎将一切学术 规范与学院礼仪丢进垃圾桶而把未来主义音乐、反乌托邦电影和赛博朋克小说 拼接到哲学话语上层出不穷地创造新形象、叠加新概念其产物便是一系列“超 信”(Hyperstitional)的虚构写作。所谓“超信”就是对即将实现的未来事实的预 言和促成是一种&quot;施行&quot;(performative)话语。这些作品包括《熔毁</span><span class=\"text_10\">毁》(Meltdown)、 </span><span class=\"text_5\">《超病毒》(</span><span class=\"text_10\">Hypervirus)、</span><span class=\"text_5\">《无未来》</span><span class=\"text_10\">(NoFuture</span><span class=\"text_5\">)和《回路》</span><span class=\"text_10\">(Circuitries)</span><span class=\"text_5\">等等。 在“加速主义”的诸多主张中最夺人眼球最荒诞不经的是它宣扬的人工智能末 世论。随着计算能力指数增长自我迭代地覆写代码的人工智能终将崛起、到达 技术奇点在计算能力、记忆力、知觉能力等领域远超人类诞生人无法理解的 超级人工智能最终反客为主地取代人类的统治地位、灭绝人类文明</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_57\"><span class=\"text_4\">形式主义的人工智能是递增的、进步的被封锁于预先指定的数据库与 专家系统的处理路径中然而连接主义或反形式主义的人工智能是爆炸性的、 伺机而动</span><span class=\"text_15\">③</span><span class=\"text_4\">的操纵时间。它在非局部的智能网络中爆发这些网络是技艺 的(technical)而不再是技术的(technological),因为它们既不依赖理论 行为又无法预测。没人知道会发生什么。图灵警察必须将网络-知觉的入侵 模拟为终极核事故堆芯熔毁失控软-自动复制源源不断地滋养社会分 裂到处都是被丢弃的肉体。即便硬件开发尚未临界也有足够的理由焦虑</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_48\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">1 </span><span class=\"calibre11\"><span class=\"text_3\">Land N. A quick and dirty introduction to accelerationism[EB/OL]. </span><span class=\"text_3\">(2017-05-25)[2021-12-01]. </span><span class=\"text_3\"></span><a href=\"https://jacobitemag.com/2017/05/25/a-quick-and-dirty-introduction-to-accelerationism\" class=\"calibre12\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text_3\">https://jacobitemag.com/2017/05/25/a-quick-and-dirty-introduction-to-accelerationism</span></a><span class=\"text_3\">. html.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_48\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre11\"><span class=\"text_3\">Land N. Fanged Noumena: Collected Writings 1987—2007[M]. Urbanomic/Sequence Press, 2012: 340-341.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000221",
