            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_47\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">3 </span><span class=\"calibre11\"><span class=\"text_3\">尽管在书的最后部分附了一篇术语表但有时这篇术语表里的解释只会让理解更混乱。</span></span></div></div></div>"
