            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_86\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">1 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">Benjamin W. Selected Writings: 1938-1940[M]. Harvard University Press, 2006: 402.</span></span></div></div></div>"
