            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_48\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre11\"><span class=\"text_3\">Le V. Philosophy's dark heir: On Nick Land's abstract horror fiction[J]. Horror Studies, 2020, 11(1): 25-42.</span></span></div></div></div>"
