            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_47\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre11\"><span class=\"text_3\">Shaviro S. No speed limit: three essays on accelerationism[M]. University of Minnesota Press, </span><span class=\"text_3\">2015. 中译见</span></span></div></div></div>"
