            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_86\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">Levi-Strauss C. The elementary structures of kinship[M]. Beacon Press, 1969: 482.</span></span></div></div></div>"
