            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_148\"><span class=\"bullet_4\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">作为本体的意志以叔本华为中介的尼采阐释</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_50\"><span class=\"text_4\">对尼克•兰德来说康德的重要性不仅在于提供了形而上学批判的典范对象, 兰德借此划定了壁垒分明的哲学史视野还在于康德开拓了许多至关重要的问题 领域。康德本人对这些问题的论述常常陷入富有张力的矛盾之中但恰恰是这些 矛盾之处打开了丰富的可能性为与康德式形而上学对立的一方提供了重要思考 资源这也反过来使康德哲学自身持续迸发着活力。在兰德看来叔本华的意志 学说是对康德哲学的第一次真正反叛并且只有以叔本华为中介才能真正理解尼 采的权力意志。尼采式的权力意志又经过巴塔耶的中介演变成兰德早期作品中 的“本体”概念这是后来的“加速主义”的哲学基础。在叔本华那里作为本 体的意志并非像康德的“物自体”那样拒绝对主体显露真容它在特定条件下会 揭开遮挡自身的“摩耶之纱”</span><span class=\"text_15\">①</span><span class=\"text_4\">。叔本华对“天才”的论述就描述了本体与人互 动的一种方式他的天才观念上承康德在“天才”上的模棱两可下启早期尼采 的狄奥尼索斯最终通向尼采式的权力意志“天才”正是被作为权力意志的“本 体”所占据的人。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_104\"><span class=\"text_5\">通过“意志”和与“意志”相关的“天才”两条线索叔本华成为康德与尼 采之间的关键转折只有理解了叔本华才能将康德与尼采放在同一个水平面上思 考使他们同台竞技、彼此反对。兰德认为倘若某人对尼采的阐释显得太过“人 性”那多半是因为他忽略了叔本华之于尼采的重要性。以此观之兰德对尼采 的理解不仅站在了海德格尔的反面也与德勒兹有相当大差异。正是对尼采的独 特理解使加速主义与流俗的人工智能威胁论和常见的种种关于未来的人道主义 理论区分开来其强劲冲击力正来自哲学史的隐蔽深渊。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_149\"><span class=\"bullet_4\">2.1 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">从康德的意志到叔本华的生命意志</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_150\"><span class=\"text_4\">要理解兰德的思想必须先理解何为“本体”。这个“本体”最初来自康德 的“物自体”被叔本华转换为“意志”最终成为尼采的“权力意志”。在意志 概念的谱系中兰德不无仓促地否定康德的地位认为康德的“意志”概念不过是 “意图的民间心理学在康德哲学中找到了巴洛克式的辩护”</span><span class=\"text_15\">②</span><span class=\"text_4\">。所谓“民间心理 学”大致是在说康德以人的“欲求”来定义“意志”相比于叔本华将意志理解 为宇宙意志或本体康德的界定似乎有点“小家子气”了。但兰德的这一判断多</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_47\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">1 </span><span class=\"calibre11\"><span class=\"text_3\">摩耶 maya 源自梵文意思是幻影、错觉叔本华以“摩耶之纱”表述人被虚幻的表象所阻碍而难以 触及作为本体的意志。</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_151\"><span class=\"bullet_3\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_16\">Land N. The Thirst for Annihilation: Georges Bataille and Virulent Nihilism[M]. Routledge, </span><span class=\"text_16\">1992: 6. </span><span class=\"text_4\">少有些草率叔本华的意志概念并非与康德哲学完全相悖而是从康德开辟的可</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_152\"><span class=\"text_5\">能性上生长起来的。本节将展示被兰德忽视的这条哲学史线索简要论述康德对 意志的论述如何影响到叔本华著名的“意志”概念。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_153\"><span class=\"text_4\">先从康德这里讲起。康德在《道德形而上学》中定义了欲求能力 BegehrungsvermOgen, faculty of desire,即“通过自己的表象而成为这些表象 的对象之原因的能力”</span><span class=\"text_15\">①</span><span class=\"text_4\">或者说一种属于主体的、能产生自己的对象的活动 而欲求若与一种产生客体的行动力结合就称之为“任意”WillkUrchoice若 非如此就只是&quot;愿望”Wunschwish。而“意志”的概念则与欲求和任意任性 相关</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_154\"><span class=\"text_5\">如果欲求能力的内在规定根据因而喜好本身是在主体的理性中发现的</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_22\"><span class=\"text_5\">那么这种欲求能力就叫做意志。所以意志就是欲求能力并不像任性</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_22\"><span class=\"text_5\">那样是与行动相关来看的而是毋宁说与使任性去行动的规定根据相关来</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_22\"><span class=\"text_5\">看的而且意志本身在自己面前而真正说来没有任何规定根据相反就理</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_143\"><span class=\"text_5\">性能够规定任性而言意志就是实践理性本身。②</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_143\"><span class=\"text_5\">实际上康德对任意、愿望和意志三个概念的区分并不牢靠</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_155\"><span class=\"text_5\">就理性能够规定一般欲求能力而言在意志之下可以包含任性但也可</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_132\"><span class=\"text_16\">以包含纯然的愿望。</span><span class=\"text_15\">③</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_22\"><span class=\"text_5\">宽泛地说可以暂时将康德的“意志”能力理解为一切“欲求”能力。但康</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_108\"><span class=\"text_5\">德必须使意志与纯粹理性的法则相关因此不得不将“意志”理解为既能产生法</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_108\"><span class=\"text_5\">则、又能产生行动的一种导向客体的能力。以此观之有行动而无法则就是“任 意”无行动、无法则而只与客体相关则就只是“愿望”。只有以道德法则为 动机的欲求才能说是“意志”即一种脱离了单纯肉体欲望的“高级欲求能力”。 康德认为这种“意志”是既能产生行动、也能产生法则的“理性”的直接产物</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_108\"><span class=\"text_5\">“纯粹理性必定自身独自就是实践的也就是可以只通过实践规则的形式来规定</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_156\"><span class=\"text_4\">意志”、“理性以一个实践法则直接规定意志……只有凭借它作为纯粹理性能够是 实践的这一点才使它是立法的成为可能。”</span><span class=\"text_15\">④</span><span class=\"text_4\">理性不但通过纯粹法则直接规定意 志其自身的运作还是一种自发的、自动的过程</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
