            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_39\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">1 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">康德李秋零.康德著作全集第4卷[M].中国人民大学岀版社北京,2005:460.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
