            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_151\"><span class=\"bullet_3\">4 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_16\">克罗斯比张红军.荒诞的幽灵现代虚无主义的根源与批判[岡.北京社会科学文献岀版社,2020: 399. </span><span class=\"text_4\">在追求完满的理想却永远无法达到平衡或满足。</span></span></div></div></div>"
