            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_39\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">5 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">康德邓晓芒.判断力批判</span><span class=\"text_5\">[M].</span><span class=\"text_5\">人民岀版社,2002: </span><span class=\"text_5\">165.</span></span></div></div></div>"
