            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_48\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">1 </span><span class=\"calibre11\"><span class=\"text_3\">尼采李秋零.不合时宜的沉思[M].华东师范大学岀版社,2007: 288.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
