            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_47\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">3 </span><span class=\"calibre11\"><span class=\"text_3\">海德格尔孙周兴王庆节.海德格尔文集尼采[M].北京商务印书馆2015: 133.</span></span></div></div></div>"
