            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_86\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">巴塔耶汪民安.色情、耗费与普遍经济乔治•巴塔耶文选[M].长春吉林人民岀版社,2003: 297.</span></span></div></div></div>"
