            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_47\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre11\"><span class=\"text_3\">巴塔耶蔡舒晓.艺术的诞生拉斯科奇迹[M].重庆西南师范大学岀版社,2019:168.</span></span></div></div></div>"
