            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_39\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">5 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">海德格尔孙周兴王庆节.海德格尔文集在通向语言的途中[M].北京商务印书馆,2015 58.</span></span></div></div></div>"
