        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_47\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">6 </span><span class=\"calibre11\"><span class=\"text_3\">特拉克尔林克.特拉克尔全集[M].重庆重庆大学岀版社,2014: 208.巴塔耶有一部著作名为《被诅咒 的部分》被诅咒的这部分是要被用来献祭、耗费的部分正如狼人是被诅咒的种族他们注定要将生命力 耗费在暴力中。</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_132\"><span class=\"text_16\">我所属的种族只知起而掠夺就像狼面对还没有被它们咬死的牲畜。</span><span class=\"text_15\">①</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_155\"><span class=\"text_5\">我从来不属于这类人我从来就不是基督徒我属于肉刑下引吭高歌的</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_21\"><span class=\"text_5\">那个族类我不懂得法律我没有道德意识我是一个粗胚你们搞错了<span class=\"tab\">      </span></span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_132\"><span class=\"text_16\">我是一匹兽我是黑奴。</span><span class=\"text_15\">②</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_50\"><span class=\"text_4\">“我从来不属于这类人我从来就不是基督徒”兰德对这段话的引用显然 是要与海德格尔对“种类”的解释针锋相对</span><span class=\"text_15\">③</span><span class=\"text_4\">。基督教的种族才是“高等种族”、 高度文明化的种族是拥有宗教上的统一性、政治上的有序性的种族与此相对 的“狼人”必定充满无视伦理道德、政治法律、文明教化的难驯野性。基督教的 核心正是对狼人所代表的毁灭性、动物性倾向的控制和引导根据德里达的分析 这种控制为纳粹提供了精神文化上的基础。兰德则暗示正是这种要控制毁灭性的 “纯一性”或“大道”而非狼人的毁灭性冲动本身才该为战争负责。他认为 战争是对狼人冲动的升华正如梦是难言欲望的升华因为战争是拥有一定的法 理或政治借口的国家与国家之间的有序争斗这种升华滋养了海德格尔所论的</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_257\"><span class=\"text_4\">“精神的烈焰”</span><span class=\"text_15\">④ </span><span class=\"text_4\">美化了通过死亡回归“本质”或“大地”的残酷战场塑造 了向死而生的英雄但同时也使真正的狼人冲动保持沉睡。力比多突破压抑的时 刻是主体同一性崩溃的时刻狼人觉醒的时刻也是战争崩溃的时刻作为战争的 结果它虽然残酷可怕但既不像海德格尔形而上学那般虚伪地美化战争也远 不如纳粹那般该为世界性的灾难负责。特拉克尔的诗歌正是要为战争“摘下面具” 裸露出不受控制的狼人冲动正如《赎罪经》里描述的那样</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_237\"><span class=\"text_5\">等到每个物摘下面具我眼中</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_237\"><span class=\"text_5\">只有恐惧绝望耻辱和瘟疫</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_237\"><span class=\"text_5\">人类的悲剧再也没有英雄</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_258\"><span class=\"text_16\">一场蹩脚戏场景是坟墓尸体</span><span class=\"text_15\">⑤</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001202": {
            "role": "text",
