        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_39\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">特拉克尔林克.特拉克尔全集[M].重庆重庆大学岀版社,2014: 208.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_40\"><span class=\"bullet_3\">3 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_16\">海德格尔孙周兴王庆节.海德格尔文集在通向语言的途中[M].北京商务印书馆,2015: 76. </span><span class=\"text_4\">老鼠吸血鬼以及狼人。”</span><span class=\"text_15\">①</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_219\"><span class=\"text_4\">但这并不是说特拉克尔就是变动不居的生成性、多样性而是说他以及他的 诗歌只是“基础差异”的效果作为基督徒的特拉克尔和作为狼人的特拉克尔或 许并没有质的区别。兰德紧接着说“或许更精确地说特拉克尔从未存在过除 非是作为一处战场一个疾病库俗用教堂的墓园作为战地医院地板上因过量 注射可卡因而奄奄一息的什么东西被基础差异的猛烈进攻骗走了清醒。”</span><span class=\"text_15\">②</span><span class=\"text_4\">。“基 础差异”(base difference)就是各种存在物与零强度之间的单向差异。零强度就 是本体就是死亡本身特拉克尔被本体的牙齿咬中于是变成了狼人狼人的 牙齿就是狼人自身永不停息地生成和变形不停寻觅着下一个猎物本体的毒 所谓狼火也随之传染扩散。一切文明都建起高大坚实的堡垒对本体的燃烧的 狼牙严阵以待。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_105\"><span class=\"bullet_4\">4.4 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">特拉克尔诗歌中的鼠群之牙</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_88\"><span class=\"text_4\">海德格尔和德里达都注意到了特拉克尔诗中的“野兽”及其所代表的毁灭性 的动物性但他们甚至等不及对诗中的动物进行最粗略的划分就匆忙将之纳入 存在的控制体系中或批判其中蕴含的毁灭倾向与纳粹的潜在关联。特拉克尔诗 中不仅有野狼或狼一样的野兽其它稀奇古怪的动物也反复现身包括黑鸟、蟾 蜍、老鼠、蝙蝠等等。除了狼人兰德还以诗中的老鼠形象作为理解特拉克尔的 关键并借此深入阐述他的本体观念这些老鼠成群结队“不可预测地快速移 动龇起沾满瘟疫的牙齿向人类嘶叫”“增强着狼人的渗透力量”</span><span class=\"text_15\">③</span><span class=\"text_4\">。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_260\"><span class=\"text_5\">特拉克尔有一首诗就以“老鼠”为名</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_243\"><span class=\"text_5\">庭院白茫茫照着秋天的月亮。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_243\"><span class=\"text_5\">从屋檐落下怪异的影子。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_243\"><span class=\"text_5\">一种沉默住在空空的窗户里</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_261\"><span class=\"text_5\">那里悄悄冒出了老鼠</span></p></div>"
        },
