            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_263\"><span class=\"text_5\">吱吱叫唤东奔西窜</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_263\"><span class=\"text_5\">一股灰色的雾气紧随</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_263\"><span class=\"text_5\">它们有异味来自厕所</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_264\"><span class=\"text_5\">它被幽灵般的月光哆嗦穿透</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_265\"><span class=\"text_5\">为了抢食发疯似的臭骂</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_265\"><span class=\"text_5\">它们一群群挤满了房子</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_265\"><span class=\"text_5\">和堆着粮食果实的仓库。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_266\"><span class=\"text_16\">冰凉的风在暗处哭诉。</span><span class=\"text_15\">①</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_260\"><span class=\"text_5\">老鼠也出现在充满狼意象的《梦魇与癫狂》中</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_172\"><span class=\"text_16\">有时他想起他的童年充满病患、恐怖和黑暗想起星星园里讳莫如深 的游戏或他在暮沉沉的院子里饲养老鼠。</span><span class=\"text_15\">②</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_267\"><span class=\"text_5\">“饲养老鼠”意味着特拉克尔不仅不厌恶似乎还愿意增强这种阴暗的动物 性力量甚至乐于看到它们在房屋的各个角落东奔西窜乐于听到它们用“吱吱 叫唤”和“发疯似的臭骂”打破空空如也的沉默这使海德格尔对特拉克尔诗歌 “大音希声”式的形而上学阐释不攻自破。兰德注意到特拉克尔诗中的鼠群大 致有如下几个特征难以定位的迅捷流动性作为载体携带虱子、保存和传播病 毒以及最重要的从内部摧毁坚固建筑的破坏性。《老鼠》一诗中的鼠群穿梭 于房屋的各个角落“一群群挤满了房子/和堆着粮食果实的仓库”已然展现了 鼠群和建筑之间的紧张关系兰德则直接将老鼠与《梦魇与癫狂》中的“祖先破 旧的家”对立起来“正是鼠群的分解内部Anteriorities的丑恶天赋给它们带来</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
