            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_39\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">1 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">特拉克尔林克.特拉克尔全集[M].重庆重庆大学岀版社,2014: 69.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
