            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_86\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">1 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">莫斯汲喆.礼物古式社会中交换的形式与理由[M].北京商务印书馆,2016: 68.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
