            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_39\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">5 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">我们在下一章再来详细讨论上帝之死。</span></span></div></div></div>"
