            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_39\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">1 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">马林诺夫斯基张云江.西太平洋上的航海者[M].北京中国社会科学岀版社,2009: 37-40.</span></span></div></div></div>"
