            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_39\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">1 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">尼采周弘.论道德的谱系一篇论战檄文[M].北京生活•读书•新知三联书店,2017: 77.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_171\"><span class=\"bullet_3\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_16\">Land N. The Thirst for Annihilation: Georges Bataille and Virulent Nihilism[M]. Routledge, </span><span class=\"text_16\">1992: 59. </span><span class=\"text_4\">待有人能来杀掉他使他返回原始的献祭中</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_224\"><span class=\"text_16\">莫非人们必须牺牲上帝本身并且出于对自身的残忍去祷拜石头、愚蠢、 困难、命运和虚无为了虚无牺牲上帝——最后一级残忍的这种悖谬的殉道 始终是留给那个现在即将到来的世系去做的我们所有人都已经认识其中的 一些了。</span><span class=\"text_15\">——①</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_312\"><span class=\"text_16\">但晚近人类出于理性而展开的极度滥用需要一场最终的献祭人类必须 抛弃理性、智力和支撑着他的大地在他心中上帝必须死去这就是他所 处的恐怖的背景这就是极限在那里他被压倒死去。只有不停歇地躲避 束缚他的贪婪人才能找到自己。</span><span class=\"text_15\">②</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_136\"><span class=\"text_5\">尼克•兰德感觉他受到了尼采和巴塔耶的鼓动怂恿。他准备动手了。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_105\"><span class=\"bullet_4\">6.3 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">上帝之死一场献祭</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_313\"><span class=\"text_5\">上帝之死必须成为一场献祭一次仪式或者至少是一出戏剧。最好将死亡 现场原样呈现在读者面前。这里的大段引用缺乏进一步解释虽然不太符合通常 的学术论文写作规范但为了使读者更近距离地体验尼克•兰德作品的疯狂冲击 力这种冒险非常值得。尼克•兰德作品的魅力是一种能传染的毒性。要使读者 充分理解本研究的意义所在最好让读者本人亲身来试尼克•兰德的毒。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_290\"><span class=\"text_5\">需要把上帝摆上祭坛将他的身体刺穿像阿兹特克人一样将他的内脏举向 太阳最后让他的尸体在祭坛上腐烂。兰德愿意做这个杀上帝的人。即便他不是 第一个也不是最后一个。即便他在杀掉上帝之前心中并非没有动摇。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_224\"><span class=\"text_16\">利奥塔试图说服他的读者如果不把上帝之死的思想当作无关紧要的事 情来对待那它只会减弱力比多的强度。上帝应该让我们厌烦到忘记而不 是激起我们的反抗。</span><span class=\"text_15\">③</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_314\"><span class=\"text_5\">对基督教只有一种理智且健康的关系完全冷漠。我不属于这种。我对 基督教信仰的憎恨耗尽了我的存在甚至耗尽了更多东西。我渴望它的上帝</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_39\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">1 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">尼采赵千帆.善恶的彼岸</span><span class=\"text_5\">[M].</span><span class=\"text_5\">北京商务印书馆,2017: </span><span class=\"text_5\">84-85.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_39\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">巴塔耶程小牧.内在经验[M].北京生活•读书噺知三联书店,2017: 243.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_131\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">3 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">Land N. The Thirst for Annihilation: Georges Bataille and Virulent Nihilism[M]. Routledge, </span><span class=\"text_5\">1992: 12.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_132\"><span class=\"text_16\">存在以便对他施暴时能感到宽慰。</span><span class=\"text_15\">①</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_139\"><span class=\"text_16\">不渴望上帝之血的无神论纯属无稽而贫血虚弱的世俗理性主义其吸 引力之微渺简直自身就是对上帝存在的论证了。萨德式的狂热表明任何 想到用钉子钉穿拿撒勒人四肢而不狂喜的人都不是无神论者只是个失望 的奴隶。</span><span class=\"text_15\">②</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_315\"><span class=\"text_5\">尼采和巴塔耶魔咒般的鼓动逼疯了兰德兰德感觉到他被虚空黑暗中的什么 东西占据了身体。匕首如狼牙般在他手中出现。兰德最后还是动了手——</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_271\"><span class=\"text_5\">我把刀刃在牛仔裤上擦了擦走进了酒吧。正值下午极其炎热静谧。 酒吧空空荡荡。我点了杯威士忌。酒保看了看血迹问道</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_154\"><span class=\"text_5\">“上帝”</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_154\"><span class=\"text_5\">“是的。”</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_316\"><span class=\"text_16\">“看来是时候有人干掉那个虚伪的小废物了总是吹嘘他老爹的权 力……</span><span class=\"text_4\">”</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_271\"><span class=\"text_5\">他笑得奸诈谄媚我一下感觉有点恶心。我虚弱地回应 “这有点病态他没有反击什么的只是一直想摸我还拉了屎像一 条狗想日你的腿。我心里有东西崩断了这哀怨一直以来把我压太低了。我 恨死那个自命不凡的小变态了。”</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_154\"><span class=\"text_5\">“所以你把他弄死了”</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_271\"><span class=\"text_5\">“是啊我杀了他白刀子进红刀子出刚一开始我就发狂了那是一 种狂喜我从来不知道自己可以这么恨。”</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_271\"><span class=\"text_5\">我感觉很平静有点头晕。威士忌味儿不错在我喉咙里蒸腾。我们沉 默了片刻。酒保平视我他焦虑得眼角抽动</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_317\"><span class=\"text_16\">“不过会有麻烦的你不觉得吗</span><span class=\"text_4\">?” </span><span class=\"text_16\">“我才不理它威胁都耗尽了我就他妈不理。” “你知道他们怎么说他老人家吗他们说是冷酷的狗杂种。残忍<span class=\"tab\">      </span></span><span class=\"text_4\">”</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_318\"><span class=\"text_5\">“我只希望我已经伤了他如果他真的存在。”</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_319\"><span class=\"text_5\">“我可不想和他过不去。”他喃喃道。 我想说“是啊这就是我们的差异。”但没力气说。风扇悠悠地转在 房里投下蜘蛛般的影子。我们又默默坐了会儿。酒保先开口</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_84\"><span class=\"text_15\"><sup class=\"calibre14\">①</sup> </span><span class=\"text_4\">Land N. The Thirst for Annihilation: Georges Bataille and Virulent Nihilism[M]. Routledge, </span><span class=\"text_4\">1992: 55.</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_131\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">Land N. The Thirst for Annihilation: Georges Bataille and Virulent Nihilism[M]. Routledge, </span><span class=\"text_5\">1992: 44.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_320\"><span class=\"text_5\">“所以上帝已经死了”</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_321\"><span class=\"text_5\">“如果那就是他。那个谎话连篇的小屁孩。我只希望这次是真的。” 酒保用舌头拨着牙心神不安</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_322\"><span class=\"text_5\">“这可是罪大恶极对吧你知道是咋回事一旦有一个条子倒下一 切都要被夷为平地直到他们找到犯事的。我的意思是你不是犯了一条法</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_323\"><span class=\"text_5\">(a law),你犯的是大法(LAW)。&quot;</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_324\"><span class=\"text_5\">我手指头蹭了下牛仔裤悬在吧台上于是一团浓浓的血块落到我的威 士忌里化开了。我笑了</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_220\"><span class=\"text_5\">“也许这是个大罪&quot;我茫茫然若有所思“但也许根本不算什么<span class=\"tab\">      </span></span><span class=\"text_5\">”尼</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_325\"><span class=\"text_5\">采写道‘<span class=\"tab\">      </span></span><span class=\"text_5\">并且我们已经杀了他'但——被赶出共同体——我渴望有点</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_325\"><span class=\"text_5\">时间单独和他待着。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_266\"><span class=\"text_16\">在完美的圣餐(</span><span class=\"text_4\">communion</span><span class=\"text_16\">)中我舔着那把沾满上帝鲜血的匕首。</span><span class=\"text_15\">①</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_260\"><span class=\"text_5\">兰德杀死了上帝他的凶器正是本体的牙齿。而后巴塔耶唱起了挽歌。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_265\"><span class=\"text_5\">含泪的幽灵</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_265\"><span class=\"text_5\">哦死去的上帝</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_265\"><span class=\"text_5\">凹陷的眼</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_265\"><span class=\"text_5\">潮湿的胡须</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_265\"><span class=\"text_5\">唯一的牙齿</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_265\"><span class=\"text_5\">哦死去的上帝</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_265\"><span class=\"text_5\">哦死去的上帝</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_265\"><span class=\"text_5\">我</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_265\"><span class=\"text_5\">我因难解的恨</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_326\"><span class=\"text_5\">而追随你</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_164\"><span class=\"text_15\"><sup class=\"calibre14\">①</sup> </span><span class=\"text_4\">Land N. The Thirst for Annihilation: Georges Bataille and Virulent Nihilism[M]. Routledge, </span><span class=\"text_4\">1992: 54-55.</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_237\"><span class=\"text_5\">我因恨而死</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_327\"><span class=\"text_5\">像一片云</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_237\"><span class=\"text_5\">消散<sup class=\"calibre13\">①</sup></span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_52\"><span class=\"text_5\">上帝被杀掉了这正是上帝想要的。上帝已经在纯粹性的永恒牢笼里囚禁太 久了他终于在被杀的瞬间触及了渴望已久的至尊性。能量不但在身体中流动 能量也构成了身体现在上帝开始腐烂腐烂意味着他终于开始归于尘土将身 体散入虚无不会又一次再一次地复活了。这也是“上帝不存在”和“上帝死了” 两个命题的区别所在。在上帝腐烂的时候世界陷入了比国王之死时更加剧烈的 终极失序。但兰德说不上有多激动但也不会后悔。一种挥之不去的使人迷惑的 恶心感始终缠绕着他使他在上帝腐烂的尸体前陷入了思考。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_203\"><span class=\"text_16\">长期以来在市场上一直有更重要的事情要谈。他们为此留着那些昂贵 的香槟。也许他们偶尔会对上帝的灭亡笑一笑但他们感觉这很烦人。甚至 他的标本剥制者也抛弃了他至少最好的那个抛弃了他。留下来的大多是无 法被雇佣者二流水平不够资格或缺乏热情。因此他仍在变得更糟 变得更千疮百孔、荒唐可笑。如果他们终究是笑了那是因为耶和华看起来 非常像一只被冷落的泰迪熊秃头一只胳膊松松垮垮一只眼睛掉出来。 当他们还是孩子关于熊的故事曾经吓到他们。再也不会了。</span><span class=\"text_15\">②</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_328\"><span class=\"text_5\">坚持不懈地为上帝寻求另一种结局是很诱人的。难道就不许他退休吗 国家肯定会给予他适当的养老金康德不是为这样的政策提供了基础吗。 毕竟很少有人会质疑衰老的暴君是悲惨的受害者。杀死上帝似乎不比宰 杀一条老得无法工作的狗更光荣。那么谁还能像尼采那样慷慨如今很少 有人会为宰杀上帝感到自豪。更常见的是一种不纯洁的含糊感觉某人因为 打扰了如此肮脏腐坏的东西而弄脏了自己。上帝曾被允许居住在我们中间 这是个尴尬之源或者说最多是一种不自在的幽默。可以理解许多人对 上帝感到隐约的不快他是不是有点太脆弱了太老了太可怜了不适合 被杀掉我们是不是该用不耐烦的“当然如此”来欢迎他的不存在并转向 更严肃的事情我们真的缺乏雅量让上帝安安静静地自己个儿地像条 狗一样死掉吗</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_39\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">1 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">巴塔耶程小牧.内在经验[M].北京生活•读书•新知三联书店,2017:191.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_131\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">Land N. The Thirst for Annihilation: Georges Bataille and Virulent Nihilism[M]. Routledge, </span><span class=\"text_5\">1992: 60.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_139\"><span class=\"text_16\">诚然我们或许值得有一个更好的上帝用以祭祀。想象一下一个孕育 了赫拉克勒斯的宇宙该有一个比西方一神教中的暴躁老猿更有尊严的统治 者这并不是没有道理。然而念叨这些遗憾毫无意义。它们属于我们历史 上令人惋惜的“已经这样了”在我们有机会货比三家地搜购上帝之前就 已被决定了。</span><span class=\"text_15\">①</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_104\"><span class=\"text_5\">大约上帝的确是死了。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_105\"><span class=\"bullet_4\">6.4 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">上帝死后人的堕胎</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_21\"><span class=\"text_5\">在上帝死后人类将能占据上帝的空位、自己统治自己吗绝非如此。上帝 是人发明出来自我延续、自我保存的工具是能量的蓄水池是限制流动的紧闭 的阀门。在上帝死后再也没有什么东西能限制人类身上的能量一去不回地流入 虚空。上帝之死预示着人之死。这个命题因福柯的《词与物》而广为人知但问 题的关键在于这里所说的“人之死”是什么意思是福柯意义上的以人为核心 的 19 世纪知识型的消失即人的知识之死吗还是尼采所重点论述的依托于基 督教上帝的、关乎负罪、内疚、责任、同情的人的道德之死这两种说法似乎都 过于轻柔了。相反尼克•兰德试图将尼采那里显露出的黑暗可能性推到极端 他提出了“为人类堕胎”的说法这暗示着终极意义上的人之死——人类文明的 终结这通向他后来宣扬的人工智能末日论。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_329\"><span class=\"text_4\">福柯所谓的“人之死”不如说是以人为核心的人道主义知识型的终结或 者通俗点说是 19 世纪特有的人类中心主义知识结构的终结。在康德式哲学人类 学意义上的人道主义知识型中在生命、劳动和语言三个领域里人既是进行表 象的独立自主的主体也是被表象的成问题的对象一切知识以及一切与知识相关 的表象都通过人而相互交织在一起人以其有限性为一切知识提供基础②。而“人 之死”不过意味着“人发现自己并不处于创造的中心并不处于空间的中间甚 至也许并非生命的顶峰和最后阶段”、“人不再是世界王国的主人、人不再在存在 的中心处进行统治”</span><span class=\"text_15\">③</span><span class=\"text_4\">以及精神分析学、结构主义人类学以及20世纪新的语言 学和文学的出现。一整套新的知识体系取代了以往较为陈旧的那套。尼采从上帝 之死中期待着超人的诞生、超人对人的克服而《词与物》中的“人之死”甚至 是从尼采位置上倒退一种不想挖断上帝之根基的谱系学、一种不想彻底终结伦</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_86\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">1 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">Land N. The Thirst for Annihilation: Georges Bataille and Virulent Nihilism[M]. Routledge, </span><span class=\"text_5\">1992: 61.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_86\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">2 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">福柯莫伟民•词与物 人文科学考古学</span><span class=\"text_5\">[M].</span><span class=\"text_5\">上海三联书店,2001: 402, 404, </span><span class=\"text_5\">410.</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_151\"><span class=\"bullet_3\">3 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_16\">福柯莫伟民•词与物 人文科学考古学[M].上海三联书店,2001: 454. </span><span class=\"text_4\">理学的认识论归根结底依然只能以人为目的而绝不会设想超人的可能性。福 柯跳出了一种人类中心主义又跳入了另一种人类中心主义直到晚年。</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_50\"><span class=\"text_4\">归根结底福柯版本的“人之死”无法回应巴塔耶版本的“上帝之死”流 动着的耗费依然被结构主义和自我美学的新建筑固定了起来。最好还是在普遍经 济学的语境中将上帝之死与人之死关联起来。汤浅博雄认为在巴塔耶那里支撑 人类存在的基础可以分为三个方面。其一作为起源与终极的统一的先验存在 即上帝他也是一切存在的目的其二为这样一个绝对统一的上帝所支撑着的 “我=我”的自我同一性这是笛卡尔“我思故我在”的命题中所包含着的上帝 其三以现在为中心、连接过去与未来的线性时间观念。</span><span class=\"text_15\">①</span><span class=\"text_4\">这就是说上帝作为 克服死亡的虚构形象发挥着两种功能首先确保服从排中律的等价交换逻辑 始终应用于维持人的自我使人的自我同一性不至于在无所限制的能量过度外流 中崩溃在这个意义上上帝约等于夸富宴中限制财物无限毁损的、能被财物交换 到的有欺骗性的“地位”。其次上帝以其永恒的无时间性维持着可度量的线性 时间观念只有在有过去也有未来的“现在”中能量的储存和再生产才是有意义 的、节约和繁衍才是有意义的。上帝是人类的支撑这是说人类依靠自我同一性 和线性时间观念才能在普遍经济的能量流中站得稳脚步自我同一性和线性时间 是未来救赎的保证未来救赎也是人类在此刻保持稳定的保险。现在上帝死了 这一切都不复存在了。人类也将消散在奔向虚无的河流中。</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_21\"><span class=\"text_5\">德勒兹在对尼采的解读中也捕捉到了人类必须死去的原因人在本质上就是</span></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c862811230e82e2a/text/000001654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><p class=\"block_330\"><span class=\"text_4\">“反动”的反动力胜利的历史就是人的历史</span><span class=\"text_15\">②</span><span class=\"text_4\">。即便人身上偶尔有能动的力 这些能动力也只是一个补充且终将转变为反动力。德勒兹绝不会承认他的尼采 解读中的辩证法倾向人的否定性将在最终的自我否定之中转化为权力意志的肯 定性。尼采《道德的谱系》已经初步说明了这个原理因为本能的内向化而自己 反对自己的人也就是那些内疚的人正由于这种自我反对而开启了新的可能性 “另一方面随着一个动物灵魂转向了自身采取了反对自身的立场地球上就 出现了一些新奇的、深邃的、前所未闻的、神秘莫测的、自相矛盾的和前途光明 的东西从而使地球本身的面貌发生了重大的变化。”</span><span class=\"text_15\">③</span><span class=\"text_4\">这一命题在《查拉图斯特 拉如是说》中被转化为“只有自我毁灭的人是值得爱的”“人身上伟大的东西正 在于他是一座桥梁而不是一个目的人身上可爱的东西正在于他是一种过渡和一 种没落”、“我爱那人”因为他“意愿没落”、“意愿挥霍”、“意愿毁灭”</span><span class=\"text_15\">④</span><span class=\"text_4\">。人的</span></p></div>"
        },
