            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c862811230e82e2a-c8b42a twpub-c862811230e82e2a-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre9\"><div class=\"block_39\"><span class=\"bullet_2\">1 </span><span class=\"calibre10\"><span class=\"text_5\">巴塔耶董澄波.文学与恶[M].北京北京燕山岀版社,2006:157.引用时依据原文有所改动。</span></span></div></div></div>"
        },
